-- Sen. Schumer: consensus on cuts in budget talks
-- 
-- Thu Apr 7, 2011 12:25pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/04/07/us-usa-budget-schumer-idUSTRE73654K20110407

 

 WASHINGTON  (Reuters) - Democratic Senator Charles Schumer said on Thursday that lawmakers have a consensus on the right level of budget cuts and where they should come from in a deal to keep the government running. 

 Schumer, a member of the Senate Democratic leadership, also said House of Representatives Speaker John Boehner, the top Republican in Congress, keeps "moving the goal post" in budget talks. (Reporting by  Andy Sullivan ; Editing by  Will Dunham )